elements.data: Your master ticket is a high-value password to manage your identity. With it, you can change sponsors, transfer ownership, setup proxies, set operator, network keys, and DNS domains. The master ticket is the secret code from which all of your other keys are derived.
How should I store this document?

This is a secret document (cryptographic property). If someone else obtains this information, they may perform unauthorized actions on your behalf.  Please store this document and/or information in a private, secure place you won’t forget.
If you need help or information, please visit the following resources.
If you lose this master ticket, you will have no way to recover this wallet or it’s proxies.
